## 5. Conclusion

This project demonstrates a fundamental truth in Scientific Machine Learning:
1. **Data alone is insufficient:** Standard deep learning diverges wildly.
2. **Physics residuals have limits:** PINNs interpolate beautifully but fail to extrapolate chaos.
3. **Continuous integration stabilizes manifolds:** Neural ODEs respect the topological boundaries of the attractor but require advanced loss functions (beyond simple MSE) to capture aperiodic chaotic transitions instead of falling into limit cycles.
